tem at the instant each disk is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.50 meter\"><math alttext=\"0.50 meter\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>0</mn><mtext>.</mtext><mn>50</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>m</mtext></math></span></span> from the center of mass?</p>\n",
